

    <div class="jumbotron text-center">
        <h1>Song App </h1>
        <p></p>
    </div>

    <p class="col text-center p-3 m-3 border border-primary bg-light">
        This App is designed for users to input songs that they like in the "Song" tab.
        <br>
        On the home page the user can query for songs based on their title, album, artist, and genre
        </p>
    </p>

    <div class="container" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;">
        <div class="bg-primary m-2 p-5 text-center w-50" style="border: black thick solid;">
        <img src="images/musicalnote.jpg" width="25%">
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <br>
    <div class="container" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;">
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byTitle">
        Show Songs By Title:
        <input type="text" name="title" 
               placeholder="Title">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    </div>
    <br>

    <br>
    <div class="container" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;">
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byAlbum">
        Show Songs By Album:
        <input type="text" name="album" 
               placeholder="Album Name">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    </div>
    <br>

    <br>
    <div class="container" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;">
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byArtist">
        Show Songs By Artist:
        <input type="text" name="artist" 
               placeholder="Artist's Name">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    </div>
    <br>

    <br>
    <div class="container" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;">
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byGenre">
        Show Songs By Genre:
        <input type="text" name="genre" 
               placeholder="Genre">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    </div>>
